        wolfram-to-atomspace
        solve-equation
        symbolic-bridge-computation
        wolfram-pattern-match
        wolfram-simplify
        wolfram-differentiate
        wolfram-integrate
        wolfram-series
        test-wolfram-bridge
        cleanup-wolfram-bridge)
